thread.title: Kim Farmer
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Kim Farmer

author: Kim Farmer
title: Kim Farmer
text: Trouble free, all prepaid, so very easy. Only thing I would point out. Car was a later model (unlike my own) and had no ignition for the key to start vehicle. I had a feeling the key just needed to be with in proximity, but didn't know the foot brake needed to be used to start. Maybe brief instructions would save this problem?
